Reasoning: The paper deals with the impact of transceiver hardware impairments on the performance of MIMO systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and communication systems (cs.COMM). The paper also analyzes the effect of impairments on large-scale MIMO systems, which falls under the category of system and control (cs.SY). The use of multiple antennas in MIMO systems is also related to networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). Finally, the paper discusses the impact of impairments on the performance of traditional MIMO systems, which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM).
